messages.messageBody:
One of my kids did that for fun one day. They wrote in one of those funny specialty fonts and then asked me if I could read it. It took me a minute to think about changing the fonts but I did eventually. It was a fun idea of a way to send secret messages. Before I read your message Sandra, I tried to change the font too, to see what it said. :-)



Angela
